  ServerId: %s
  Request: %s (%s)
  Serialization took: %.06f
  ServerTime: %.06f
  Deserialization: %.06f
  CallbackTime: %s"
             server-id
             method
             id
             (float-time (time-subtract before-send start-time))
             (float-time (time-subtract received-time before-send))
             (float-time (time-subtract after-parsed-time received-time))
